{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-036","title":"Sentence 36","sectionId":"sentences-031","sectionTitle":"Sentence 31-40","pageStart":244,"pageEnd":248,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":51,"duplicateEntryCount":1,"pages":[{"number":244,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 36"},{"type":"text","text":"Their streamlined bodies, the absence of hind legs, and the presence"},{"type":"text","text":"of a fluke and blowhole cannot disguise their affinities with land dwelling"},{"type":"text","text":"mammals."},{"type":"text","text":"它们呈流线型的身体，后腿的消失，尾片和气孔的出现，这些"},{"type":"text","text":"特征都不能掩饰它们和陆生哺乳动物的相似之处。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是“Their bodies, the absence of ..., and the presence of ..."},{"type":"text","text":"cannot disguise their affinities with ...”。句子的主语较长，由三个名词短"},{"type":"text","text":"语构成。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"streamline /ˈstriːmlaɪn/ vt. 使成流线型","headword":"streamline"},{"type":"entry","text":"absence /ˈæbsəns/ n. 缺席；缺乏","headword":"absence"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 ab（离去）+sen（t）（送）+ce→送走→缺席"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 absence of mind心不在焉"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 lack n. 缺乏"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 absent a. 缺席的"},{"type":"entry","text":"hind /haɪnd/ a. 后面的，在后的","headword":"hind"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 后面的（behind）的后面（hind）"},{"type":"entry","text":"presence /ˈprezns/ n. 存在；出现","headword":"presence"}]},{"number":245,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"搭配 in the presence of sth. 有…的存在"},{"type":"note","text":"反义 absence n. 缺席；缺乏"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 present a. 当前的；存在的"},{"type":"entry","text":"fluke /fluːk/ n. 尾片","headword":"fluke"},{"type":"entry","text":"blowhole /ˈbloʊhoʊl/ n. （鲸头顶的）呼吸孔","headword":"blowhole"},{"type":"entry","text":"disguise /dɪsˈɡaɪz/ vt./n. 掩饰；伪装","headword":"disguise"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 dis（分离）+guise（外表）→使看不到真实的外表→掩饰；"},{"type":"text","text":"伪装"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 mask vt. 掩饰"},{"type":"text","text":"pretend vt. 伪装"},{"type":"text","text":"conceal vt. 隐蔽；隐瞒"},{"type":"entry","text":"affinity /əˈfɪnəti/ n. （语言、生物等之间的）类同，近似","headword":"affinity"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 af（表加强）+fin（界限）+ity→进入范围内→密切关系"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 infinity n. 无限的时间或空间；无穷"},{"type":"entry","text":"dwell /dwel/ vi. 居住","headword":"dwell"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 reside vi. 居住；（性质等）存在"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 dwelling n. 住宅，住所"},{"type":"text","text":"dweller n. 居民，居住者"},{"type":"entry","text":"mammal /ˈmæml/ n. 哺乳动物","headword":"mammal"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 mamma（妈妈）+l→靠吃妈妈的奶长大→哺乳动物"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 mammalian a. 哺乳动物的，哺乳纲的"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"}]},{"number":246,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"常见哺乳动物："},{"type":"entry","text":"antelope /ˈæntɪloʊp/ n. 羚羊","headword":"antelope"},{"type":"entry","text":"anthropoid /ˈænθrəpɔɪd/ n. 类人猿","headword":"anthropoid"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 anthropology n. 人类学"},{"type":"entry","text":"baboon /bæˈbuːn/ n. 狒狒","headword":"baboon"},{"type":"entry","text":"bat /bæt/ n. 蝙蝠","headword":"bat"},{"type":"entry","text":"beaver /ˈbiːvər/ n. 海狸","headword":"beaver"}]},{"number":247,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"beluga /bəˈluːɡə/ n. 白鲸","headword":"beluga"},{"type":"entry","text":"buffalo /ˈbʌfəloʊ/ n. 水牛","headword":"buffalo"},{"type":"entry","text":"camel /ˈkæml/ n. 骆驼","headword":"camel"},{"type":"entry","text":"cetacean /sɪˈteɪʃn/ n. 鲸目动物（其中有些是地球上最大的动物）","headword":"cetacean"},{"type":"entry","text":"chimpanzee /ˌtʃɪmpænˈziː/ n. 黑猩猩","headword":"chimpanzee"},{"type":"entry","text":"dolphin /ˈdɑːlfɪn/ n. 海豚","headword":"dolphin"},{"type":"entry","text":"donkey /ˈdɔːŋki/ n. 驴","headword":"donkey"},{"type":"entry","text":"elk /elk/ n. 麋鹿","headword":"elk"},{"type":"entry","text":"fox /fɑːks/ n. 狐","headword":"fox"},{"type":"entry","text":"gibbon /ˈɡɪbən/ n. 长臂猿","headword":"gibbon"},{"type":"entry","text":"giraffe /dʒəˈræf/ n. 长颈鹿","headword":"giraffe"},{"type":"entry","text":"gorilla /ɡəˈrɪlə/ n.